{"tid":1001290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"製作公司拒製眾志標誌產品","createTime":"2019-01-30T04:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T05:01:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3140cdd5ee75c855cbc75b5819af2be32dfda8a6","tid":1001290,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190130/20602265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190130%2F20602265&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=169240ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190130%2F20602265&h=01f71732\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190130/20602265</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月30日 <br />\n<br />\n製作公司拒製眾志標誌產品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190130/large/30la6p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190130%2Flarge%2F30la6p5.jpg&h=e50624e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】維園年宵市場今開鑼，多個政黨擺檔售賣產品籌款及宣傳，但政治打壓無孔不入，被封鎖議會之路的香港眾志今年製作年宵產品再遇阻礙，稱印製有眾志名稱及標誌的布袋（圖）時兩度被拒，眾志引述印製公司職員指廠房收到政府批文，眾志的中英文名及標誌一律不得印製，質疑當局有政治黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陳校長領師生義賣豬仔<br />\n<br />\n稱收政府禁令<br />\n<br />\n眾志以「今年不再做港豬」為主題的布袋製作障礙重重，眾志指首間接洽的製作公司拒印有眾志標誌的設計圖，轉公司後同被拒，眾志引述該公司職員透露廠方收到政府批文，有一系列字樣及圖案不得印製，包括眾志標誌及中英文名稱，最終眾志刪去標誌方能成功製作。<br />\n<br />\n眾志主席林朗彥指，接洽兩間公司都是香港公司，首間表明不接任何政黨定單，第二間則指收到政府批文不准印眾志標誌，但指該公司未有透露批文來自香港或中國政府及廠房位置，最終眾志改設計圖，同一廠房亦拒印，該公司後另找廠房印製新設計才成事。林批評不論中、港政府不能限制政黨的合法活動，又指有廠商避免印製一切政治產品，主因建制派抹黑反對派主張，造成自我審查氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁穎妍  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n陳校長領師生義賣豬仔<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n外派員宜居城市　港跌至41位<br />\n<br />\n陳校長領師生義賣豬仔<br />\n靚桃花難求　加價五成乾貨檔豬多選擇　求豬籠入水"},{"pid":"a3d3f6c8dbce68f5b9c07f2d20481fbdece59f15","tid":1001290,"uid":16846,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"一班豬呼籲人唔好做港豬係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4650dee94777bb14ba6d7cef4d22338a0f2b8b","tid":1001290,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3d3f6c8dbce68f5b9c07f2d20481fbdece59f15","tid":1001290,"uid":16846,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"一班豬呼籲人唔好做港豬係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:48:47.000Z","msg":"到底係邊間公司？"},{"pid":"56680492b4cb3fc125c204aa9a0e7d4550060eb1","tid":1001290,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"文字獄了"},{"pid":"2fdc7930e84dd8a62cf472a3ef474bd5bd806d99","tid":1001290,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a3d3f6c8dbce68f5b9c07f2d20481fbdece59f15","tid":1001290,"uid":16846,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"一班豬呼籲人唔好做港豬係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"全兒登最on9 就係你依種波台生滋狗， 學咩人類笑人港豬？"},{"pid":"f8d30df2fc12bd45b7b0a998e306f773149a6839","tid":1001290,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">之前有鋪頭唔做gay佬生意<br />\nchild登仔好撐<br />\n話係商業自由㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"0fe14fef2a9a598c85451392016b479110d3e13b","tid":1001290,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:01:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da7f416a7defc18b5750872b8d46f0b4db84d241","tid":1001290,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}